textDelta: In life, there are days when you're a winner and days when you're a loser.
There is nothing that can prepare you for the game that we call life.
One of the best ways to succeed at life is to build a great team around you.
Coming up with a good strategy will help you succeed in life.
Understanding the rules of life can be a very key asset.
